Emery: &quot;We started well with the first goal and then they had the difference with attacking moments, determination &amp; quality. We couldn't stop this moment. The second half we wanted to little by little impose ourselves to find one goal but another penalty closed the match.&quot;<br />
<br />
Unai Emery: [It is a] Bad result. This loss we can use to be better. We know we need to defensively get better. Liverpool have progressed a lot and it is an example for us. We need to do this progress.&quot;

